      <title>旧的共同职位自2019年以来的最高利润在保费增长方面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/old-mutual-posts-highest-profit-since-2019-on-premium-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Old Mutual Group Ltd.报告了其自2019年以来的最高利润，这是由于其对南非家里的短期保险和财富管理产品的需求不断增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/old-mutual-posts-highest-profit-since-2019-on-premium-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 05:27:48 GMT</pubDate>
